  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut all the <strong>potatoes</strong> to roughly equal size (approx. 4cm chunks)</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>potatoes</strong> and <strong>salt</strong> (optional) to a large pot of <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Boil for 15 min or until you can pierce them easily with a fork</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, place your hand flat onto each&nbsp;<strong>chicken breast fillet</strong>&nbsp;and slice in half as if you were cutting a burger bun, so you are left with two thinner pieces</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crack the <strong>egg<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;into a shallow bowl and beat well with a fork</p>\r\n<p>Add 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span><strong>&nbsp;flour</strong>&nbsp;to a plate and season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>On a second plate, add the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Coat&nbsp;each piece of <strong>chicken</strong> in the seasoned <strong>flour</strong>, tapping off any excess</p>\r\n<p>Dip it in the <strong>egg</strong> and coat well</p>\r\n<p>Roll it in the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and make sure it is evenly coated</p>\r\n<p>Repeat with the rest of the <strong>chicken</strong> and set aside &ndash; these are your <strong>chicken escalopes</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>broccoli</strong> into florets (including the stalk)</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>broccoli</strong> to the potato pot, and boil for a further 5 min&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and roughly chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bash the <strong>garlic</strong> with 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>salt</strong> in a <strong>pestle &amp; mortar</strong> until you have a smooth paste</p>\r\n<p>Melt 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>butter</strong> in a pot with the garlic paste</p>\r\n<p>Once the <strong>butter</strong>&nbsp;has started to foam, remove the pot from the heat and set aside &ndash; this is your <strong>garlic butter</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with&nbsp;1-2 tbsp&nbsp;<strong>vegetable oil</strong>&nbsp;over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p>Once&nbsp;hot, add the <strong>chicken escalopes</strong> and cook for 5 min on each side, or <span class=\"text-highlight\">until golden</span> brown and cooked through</p>\r\n<p>Transfer&nbsp;them to a piece of kitchen towel</p>\r\n<p>Season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper&nbsp;</strong>&ndash; this is your <strong>breadcrumbed chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/292__-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and mash the <strong>broccoli</strong> and <strong>potatoes</strong> with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a splash of <strong>milk</strong></p>\r\n<p>Serve with the <strong>breadcrumbed chicken</strong> and the <strong>garlic butter</strong> to the side</p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 8,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    }
